    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325610/extras/014cffb1eb260ac027c75e092c6b211f.poster.avif?t=1761310431\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325610/extras/014cffb1eb260ac027c75e092c6b211f.webm?t=1761310431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325610/extras/014cffb1eb260ac027c75e092c6b211f.mp4?t=1761310431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在永恒与明日的夹缝中，暮昏餐厅供应世间罕见的珍馐佳肴。作为这家餐厅的新任主人，你的日子充满了为客人填饱肚子、与他们推心置腹的对话。这是一种平静而祥和的生活。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >直到某天，一位常客的头颅竟然出现在待上桌的甜品中，打破了这份平静。现在，你成了头号嫌疑人！在这片时间停滞的奇异之地，你能揭开谜团，洗清嫌疑吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325610/extras/4a0c89f0352e23a15d49deec6a756b2e.poster.avif?t=1761310431\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325610/extras/4a0c89f0352e23a15d49deec6a756b2e.webm?t=1761310431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325610/extras/4a0c89f0352e23a15d49deec6a756b2e.mp4?t=1761310431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>纵情于异界盛宴</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在无尽暮昏王国中大饱眼福（偶尔也用眼睛下菜，大饱口福），品味那些不可思议的奇幻甜点。为愈发挑剔的客人们搜罗愈发稀有的食材，精进你的厨艺，让暮昏餐厅蓬勃发展！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325610/extras/3d4824146deb475482e0c73875c1944f.poster.avif?t=1761310431\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325610/extras/3d4824146deb475482e0c73875c1944f.webm?t=1761310431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325610/extras/3d4824146deb475482e0c73875c1944f.mp4?t=1761310431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>构筑永恒的羁绊</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >了解你的顾客，也探索内心的自己 :) 认识一群天界的友人（或恶魔），稍微偷窥一下他们的秘密，赚取丰厚的小费！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325610/extras/ca396f2082a5112f393c7768a508adbd.poster.avif?t=1761310431\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325610/extras/ca396f2082a5112f393c7768a508adbd.webm?t=1761310431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325610/extras/ca396f2082a5112f393c7768a508adbd.mp4?t=1761310431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>谋杀嫌疑？别想太多！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们几乎可以确定你没有杀那个家伙……至少有80%的把握。所以，利用你作为顶级厨师和顾问的身份，找出真正的凶手！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325610/extras/cc4b6d65fa17d17d99d6432db30d4ab1.poster.avif?t=1761310431\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325610/extras/cc4b6d65fa17d17d99d6432db30d4ab1.webm?t=1761310431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325610/extras/cc4b6d65fa17d17d99d6432db30d4ab1.mp4?t=1761310431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>小游戏！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >毕竟，游戏总得有点游戏性嘛！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >别忘了！顾客永远是对的。</p>",
